title: A few so22/so33 pieces I'm looking for

posts.content:
Hi
I'm looking for a few parts for a so22/so33 interior I have to complete it and make it more usable for our family. I was just wondering if any body has any of these items spare maybe .

I need a interior table or any pieces from the frame would be great
A cargo door table leg or complete table (found)
The front most seat headrest bar
2 original back rest pieces the wooden bits and the metal fittings
And any old orange plaid
Many thanks ben
